result.description: Specify the name of the brand under which the product is produced. If the product does not have a brand, use the value 'No brand'.
result.name: Brand

result.description: Select the most suitable product type. By type, products are categorized on the Ozon website. If the type is incorrect, the product will fall into the wrong category. To specify the type correctly, find products similar to yours on the Ozon website and see what type they have specified.
result.name: Type

result.description: Specify the name of the product model. Do not specify the type and brand in this field.
result.name: Model Name (to combine products into one PDP)

result.description: Specify links to the photos, separated by commas, which show the product at different equal angles. It is important to follow the sequence in a series of photos so that the angle of each subsequent photo differs from the previous one by an equal angle. A 3D model of the product will be automatically formed from these photos on the site. The minimum recommended amount is 15 pieces.
result.name: 3D Image

result.description:
The name is written according to the principle:
Type + Brand + Model (series + explanation) + Manufacturer Article Code + , (comma) + Attribute
The name is not written in capital letters (do not use caps lock).
A comma is placed before the attribute. If there are several attributes, they are also separated by commas.
If there is no component of the name, skip it.
The attribute can be: color, weight, volume, number of pieces per package, etc.
Color is written with a small letter.
Do not write the word "color" in the name.
There is no period at the end.
Do not use any punctuation marks other than a comma.
Quotation marks are used for names in Russian only.
Examples of correct names:
Smartphone Apple iPhone XS MT572RU/A, space black 
Dr. Martens Sneakers Movie Classics, white and black, size 43
Washing Powder Ariel White Magic with a measuring spoon, 15 kg
Sauce Heinz Xtreme Tabasco Super Hot, 10 ml
Toy for pets Four Paws Running Mouse BMM, white
result.name: Name

result.description: Description of the product, marketing text. Must be completed in Russian.

result.description: Item weight without package (net weight) in grams per 1 SKU. It is permissible to specify only numbers.
result.name: Item Weight, g

result.description: The alphanumeric code of the product for its accounting is unique among the brand's products. It is not an EAN/serial number/barcode, not equal to the name of the product model - there are separate attributes for these parameters. The article code is displayed in the product description page on the website and can be used in the automatic formation of the product name.
result.name: Seller code

result.description: IMPORTANT!!! A sign for products that contain erotica, sex scenes, images with obscene expressions, even if they are written partially or with special symbols, as well as for products of category 18+ (only for adults).
result.name: 18+ Sign

result.description: Specify a hazard class (1-9) or \Not dangerous\. Select one value from the drop-down list. Once the item is created, you won't be able to edit this attribute.
result.name: Product Hazard Class

result.description:
Specify the base or dominant color of your product by selecting a value from the list. If you don't find an exact match, use the closest similar colors. 

Complex colors should be described by listing simple colors. For example, if you describe a bumblebee, it obviously has black, yellow and white colors, and you can indicate them all by a simple enumeration. 

Remember that the Product Color attribute is the base color. You can specify other colors in the Color Name attribute.
result.name: Product color

result.description: Add an extended description of the product with photos and videos from the template in JSON format. Read more: https://seller-edu.ozon.ru/docs/work-with-goods/dobavlenie-rich-kontenta-json.html
result.name: JSON Rich Content

result.description:
How many sales packages have you put together and now sell as one SKU.

If your product is 24 jars of baby puree sealed in 1 package at a factory and this product can be sold in the same form in other stores, the value of the attribute will be 1.

If your product is 3 light bulbs sealed or linked in one package by you and you decided to combine them yourself (and a plant produces bulbs in packages of, for example, 1 pc and 10 pcs), the value of the attribute will be 3.
result.name: Number of Sales Packages

You can read more about the merger in the series here https://seller-edu.ozon.ru/work-with-goods/zagruzka-tovarov/created-goods/obedinenie-tovarov-v-seriu
